{"tid":975912,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[又係LG]用 2 年前舊 U 太 OUT？LG G7 Fit 開賣，配 S821 賣呢個價","createTime":"2019-01-10T04:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:24:28.000Z","uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"6d2ef7a3047cb79b7feefe8b34631ae6b0d3dcb8","tid":975912,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T04:48:42.000Z","msg":"On撚9，d 821死貨去唔晒?<br />\n2019仲賣821<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n821又熱又晒電<br />\n<br />\n沉寂咗好耐無出新機的 LG，終於再有新機抵港！是咁的，打開 Facebook，就剛巧見到豐澤出 post，表示 G7 Fit 接受預訂喎，呢部到底係一部點樣嘅手機，同時又會賣幾錢，幾時開賣，同有乜送啦！就等版主話畀大家知！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用 2 年前舊 U 太 OUT？LG G7 Fit 開賣，配 S821 賣呢個價<br />\n<br />\nLG G7 Fit 現已接受預訂，建議零售價為 $2998，將於 1 月 11 日正式開賣。距離開賣日只有兩天，但依然會有早鳥優惠，除咗會送保護殼同保護貼，仲會送 6 個月屏幕保 / 64GB microSD 卡 / 10000mAh 尿袋 (3 選 2)。$2998 呢個價，抵唔抵呢？繼續睇落去！<br />\n<br />\n用 2 年前舊 U 太 OUT？LG G7 Fit 開賣，配 S821 賣呢個價<br />\n<br />\n講到呢部 G7 Fit，其實真心係一部好奇怪的手機，2019 年出，但卻用 2 年前嘅處理器。係呀，佢除咗有 6.1 吋 19.5:9 屏幕之外，最神奇係佢居然配備 Qualcomm S821 處理器，2 年前嘅旗艦 U，放落呢部定位中階的手機，又有無睇頭？另外，G7 Fit 亦內置 4GB RAM 以及 64GB ROM，並用上 16MP 單鏡頭，支持 32-bit Quad DAC、3.5mm 耳機輸出、IP68 防塵防水和 MIL-STD-810G 標準。你對佢，有無興趣呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4531/212156/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4531%2F212156%2F1%2F&d=NJS9iWJNrGuYhPFqm1V0FPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=517a0c71\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4531/212156/1/</a>"},{"pid":"cfc48acdc5bc42b294297ebefc9670bd117711aa","tid":975912,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T06:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffa52ff8c4898aa9cd01eee595641ba6f7e10ee","tid":975912,"uid":61675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T06:43:16.000Z","msg":"三星a7 粒垃圾u 都賣2998 啦"},{"pid":"593